snippet.title: SHAUNZ SAYS: DOMESTIC VIOLENCE IN THE CASE OF JOHHNY DEPP & AMBER HEARD Let's talk/ Shaunz World
snippet.description:
Heya loves! I'll be giving my views on domestic abuse/violence. It's something that so many people experience and it needs to stop! Hear my thoughts. What are yours?

Hope you've enjoyed listening, i tried not to make it too hot and heavy, but i'd like to talk with you guys in the comments. Thanks for watching, please subscribe, thumbs up, comment and share..xoxoxo

#domesticviolence #notodomesticabuse
